#, javascript-format
msgid ""
"Pixelplanet fulfills the OpenID Connect (OIDC) specifications. So an "
"application that supports OIDC could ask for consent and login using "
"pixelplanet accounts. The required endpoints can be auto-discovered via the $"
"{ wellKnownUrl } URL."
msgstr ""
"Pixelplanet 符合 OpenID Connect (OIDC) 规范。因此，支持 OIDC 的应用程序可以请"
"求用户授权并使用 Pixelplanet 帐户登录。可以通过 ${ wellKnownUrl } URL 自动发"
"现所需的端点。"

